OL,3,CAmanda Knox reveals her kids play
OL,4,C'mummy in jail' games
OL,6,FAmanda Knox has told ITV News' What
OL,7,FYou Need To Know podcast her children
OL,8,Fnow reenact being "mummy in prison" in
OL,9,FItaly, as she opened up on the
OL,10,Fchallenges of parenting in the shadow
OL,11,Fof public suspicion.
OL,13,FIn a deeply personal conversation with
OL,14,Fhost Lucy Watson, the American also
OL,15,Frevealed she wants to visit Meredith
OL,16,FKercher's grave and grieve with the
OL,17,FKercher family, who she has still
OL,18,Fnever met.
