OL,6,FAnd she explained how her release from
OL,7,Fprison after being exonerated for the
OL,8,FBritish student's 2007 murder in
OL,9,FPerugia did not mark the end of her
OL,10,Fordeal, but the beginning of a
OL,11,Flifelong struggle to reclaim her
OL,12,Fidentity and freedom.
OL,14,FOn explaining her past to her children:
OL,16,F"I believe that to be the best parent
OL,17,Fthat I can be, I need to be
OL,18,Ftransparent and I need to be age
OL,19,Fappropriately honest. They are a bit
OL,20,Flittle at the moment.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/12
