OL,6,F"But what I can say is that 'when
OL,7,Fmummy was young, mummy went to go
OL,8,Fstudy in a foreign country, and it was
OL,9,Fbeautiful. And she made friends. And
OL,10,Fthen out of the blue, someone hurt her
OL,11,Ffriend really badly. And they thought
OL,12,Fmummy hurt her friend. And so they put
OL,13,Fmummy in jail. And then mummy had to
OL,14,Fprove that she was innocent, and she
OL,15,Fgot out of prison and she's gone on
OL,16,Fwith her life. She met Papa, she had
OL,17,Fyou, The End, basically.'"
OL,19,FOn how her daughter now plays 'mummy
OL,20,Fin prison' games:
