OL,3,CAmanda Knox reveals her kids play
OL,4,C'mummy in jail' games
OL,6,F"At this point, it's really simple
OL,7,Fbecause three-year-olds have the
OL,8,Fattention span that they have. But
OL,9,Fit's been really interesting seeing
OL,10,Fher process that because to her
OL,11,Fstories are games. And she'll now want
OL,12,Fto play 'mummy goes to Italy with me'.
OL,14,F"So she'll have me reenact being
OL,15,Fbehind prison bars or she'll pretend
OL,16,Fto be mummy. Like if we see a
OL,17,Fplayground where they have the bars,
OL,18,Fshe'll be like, 'oh look, I'm mummy in
OL,19,Fprison.' She is processing the way
OL,20,Fchildren process things, which is
OL,21,Fthrough play."
