OL,6,FOn life after prison:
OL,8,F"I discovered, upon being released
OL,9,Ffrom prison, that I did not get to go
OL,10,Fback to being an anonymous person,
OL,11,Fthat I was forever branded the girl
OL,12,Faccused of murder. My very identity
OL,13,Fhad become wrapped up and mixed
OL,14,Ftogether with the death of my friend.
OL,16,F"What does it mean to be free is
OL,17,Fsomething that I have spent my entire
OL,18,Fadult life contemplating, having had
OL,19,Fmy freedom stolen from me."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/12
