OL,6,FOn not being able to speak to Meredith
OL,7,FKercher's family:
OL,9,F"I've literally never had access to
OL,10,FMeredith's family, ever. I've never
OL,11,Fmet them. They don't know who I am,
OL,12,Fand they only know me through the
OL,13,Fworst context possible.
