OL,6,F"However, what I will say is that it
OL,7,Fis not uncommon in cases of wrongful
OL,8,Fconviction for family members of the
OL,9,Ffirst and primary victim to hang on to
OL,10,Fthis sense of assuming guilt of the
OL,11,Fexonerated person, thinking that they
OL,12,Fwouldn't have been accused in the
OL,13,Ffirst place if they weren't actually,
OL,14,Fyou know, in some way guilty of
OL,15,Fsomething.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/12
