OL,4,C'mummy in jail' games
OL,6,F"But I think the other thing that
OL,7,FMeredith's family is grappling with is
OL,8,Fthe fact that this case spiraled out
OL,9,Fof control very quickly and discerning
OL,10,Fthe truth about what happened to
OL,11,FMeredith very, very quickly became
OL,12,Fsecondary to the scandalous narrative
OL,13,Fthat was unfolding about the case and
OL,14,Fthe vilification of me.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/12
