OL,6,F"And I think one of their complaints
OL,7,Fthat I 100% agree with is that when
OL,8,Fpeople think of this case, they don't
OL,9,Fremember Meredith's name, they
OL,10,Fremember mine. They don't even
OL,11,Fremember the murderer's name, they
OL,12,Fremember mine. And if this case had
OL,13,Fbeen investigated and prosecuted and
OL,14,Fwritten about publicly properly, no
OL,15,Fone would ever know who I was. It 100%
OL,16,Fbothers me (some people still don't
OL,17,Fthink I'm innocent). It very much
OL,18,Fbothers me."
