OL,7,Fhad in my life was the opportunity to
OL,8,Fgrieve her, to visit her grave and to
OL,9,Fgrieve her and to share those moments
OL,10,Fwith her family. And to share in that
OL,11,Fgrief because I think, even more than
OL,12,Fme, a life defining tragedy happened
OL,13,Fto them."
